## ABOUT ME 
Hello, my name is Lisa Zhang. I am currently a senior and this will be my last year as a student at Phillip and Sala Burton High School. I am involve in many clubs and academies such as the Academy of Arts Media and Entertainment, Red Cross Club, CYC/YCE, International Club, and the Advanced Meditation Crew. On my spare time, I like to volunteer at local buildings and events, take and edit pictures, spend quality time with my friends, and cook/bake at home.
